    "body": "FFmpeg path resolution was checking the system `PATH` first, which caused `@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg` and user config to be silently ignored whenever `ffmpeg` existed on the system.\n\n## Changes\n\n- **`packages/core/src/utils/system/ffmpeg.ts`**: Reorder initialization to match intended priority:\n  - **Before (wrong):** system env → `@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg` → user config\n  - **After (correct):** `@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg` → user config → system env (implicit fallback via default `'ffmpeg'`/`'ffprobe'`/`'ffplay'` values)\n\n```typescript\n// Before — system PATH check short-circuited the whole chain\nconst env = await exec('ffmpeg -version', { booleanResult: true })\nif (!env) {\n  try { /* @karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg */ }\n  catch { /* user config */ }\n}\n\n// After — managed plugin takes priority; system PATH is implicit fallback\ntry {\n  const plugin = await import('@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg')\n  // use plugin paths\n} catch {\n  // fall back to user config; default 'ffmpeg' string resolves via system PATH\n}\n```\n\n<!-- START COPILOT ORIGINAL PROMPT -->\n\n\n\n<details>\n\n<summary>Original prompt</summary>\n\n> \n> ----\n> \n> *This section details on the original issue you should resolve*\n> \n> <issue_title>Bug: 获取ffmpeg文件顺序问题</issue_title>\n> <issue_description>### 描述问题\n> \n> 初始化ffmpeg的时候，顺序应该是：可管理版本的@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg -> 用户配置 -> 系统环境变量\n> \n> ### 复现步骤\n> \n> 1. 第一步\n> 2. 第二步\n> 3. ...\n> \n> \n> ### 预期行为\n> \n> 初始化ffmpeg的时候，顺序应该是@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg -> 用户配置 -> 系统环境变量\n> \n> ### 实际行为\n> \n> 系统环境变量 -> @karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg -> 用户配置\n> \n> ### 操作系统\n> \n> win11\n> \n> ### Node.js 版本\n> \n> 24\n> \n> ### 项目版本\n> \n> 114514\n> \n> ### 附加信息\n> \n> _No response_</issue_description>\n> \n> ## Comments on the Issue (you are @copilot in this section)\n> \n> <comments>\n> </comments>\n> \n\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n<!-- START COPILOT CODING AGENT SUFFIX -->\n\n- Fixes KarinJS/Karin#628\n\n<!-- START COPILOT CODING AGENT TIPS -->\n---\n\n🔒 GitHub Advanced Security automatically protects Copilot coding agent pull requests. You can protect all pull requests by enabling Advanced Security for your repositories. [Learn more about Advanced Security.](https://gh.io/cca-advanced-security)\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nBug Fixes:\n- 修复：即使系统中存在 ffmpeg 可执行文件，也能确保 ffmpeg 的初始化遵循 `@karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg` 和用户自定义路径设置。\n\n<details>\n<summary>Original summary in English</summary>\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nBug Fixes:\n- Ensure ffmpeg initialization respects @karinjs/plugin-ffmpeg and user-defined paths even when system ffmpeg binaries are present.\n\n</details>",
